    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You magically distract the triggering creature and turn its momentary uncertainty into encouragement for another creature. The triggering creature must reroll the <strong>d20 </strong>and use the lower roll.</p>\n<p>You can then choose a different creature you can see within range (you can choose yourself). The chosen creature has <strong>advantage </strong>on the next attack roll, ability check, or saving throw it makes within 1 minute. A creature can be empowered by only one use of this spell at a time.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Bard, Sorcerer, Wizard</p>",
